title: A1466 820-00165-A no power on
message:
Hi, I have an A1466 820-00165-A that has no power.
It has greenlight, fan spin, consumes around 300 mA on bench PSU, CPU gets hot, all big coils have voltage, but it does not have usb activity.

It had some corrosion on the U7600 and so i replaced, and R8164 was blouwn and i replaced it too but still no power.
Now I get 1.05V on pin 2 of U7600, but when i measure P1V05S0_PGOOD on R8164 it shuts down.

Can you help?

title: A1466 820-00165-A no power on
message:
It worked with a new BIOS.
TKS!
